snippet.title: AEW: Fight Forever - Official HOOKHausen: Very Handsome, Very Evil Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for AEW: Fight Forever to see what to expect with the HOOKHAUSEN: Very Handsome, Very Evil DLC pack, which features AEW stars HOOK and Danhausen as playable wrestlers. The HOOKHAUSEN: Very Handsome, Very Evil DLC pack will be available now on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and PC, and it will be available on Nintendo Switch on October 5, 2023. 

The HOOKHAUSEN bundle is also included in the AEW: Fight Forever Season Pass and AEW: Fight Forever Elite Edition.
